attributes.description: Provide an overview and statistics of the audit trail of all HTTP requests that the Microsoft Graph service received and processed.

params.markdown:
**Navigation**

[Integrations Page](/app/integrations/detail/azure/overview?integration=graphactivitylogs)    

**Overview**

This dashboard provides an overall view of Microsoft Graph Activity Logs. It provides insights into total requests made by applications and API clients in your tenant, while also breaking down the activity by Cloud Region, Users, and HTTP Methods.
